divs: Sighting DetailsWas at dinner in Nelson, New Zealand. Was enjoying the sunset so took 2 digital pics of it. Only later while looking at the pics on my computer I realized there was something else in the photos. This is when I saw the four lights. The horizontal lines above are overhead power lines.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Nelson
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Four round lights grouped together in pics of sunset.
